Executive Profile
Charles P. Cooley  Vice President and Treasurer, Noveon Kalama, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships61--
Background

		Mr. Charles P. Cooley, also known as Charile, serves as a Vice President and Treasurer of Noveon Kalama, Inc. Mr. Cooley served as Senior Vice President of Lubrizol Corporation from July 2004 to September 16, 2011 and as its Chief Financial Officer from 1998 to September 16, 2011. He joined Lubrizol in 1998 and served as its Vice President from April 1998 to July 2005 and also served as its Treasurer from September 2006 to April, 2009. He served as Assistant Treasurer ... of Corporate Finance at Atlantic Richfield Company. He served as Vice President of Finance at ARCO Products Company. He has been a Director of Modine Manufacturing Company since October 18, 2006 and KeyCorp. since November 17, 2011. Mr. Cooley received his M.B.A. from Dartmouth College's Amos Tuck School of Business Administration and a B.A. degree in Philosophy from Yale University.Read Full Background




